channel.title: Glitched Prayers
channel.description: I am using a 508/525 PulsePk source. It was originally meant to have turmoil, soulsplit, and leechs. I changed it to a 508 client because I like old school servers and now Piety and Smite have Turmoil and Soul Split sounds. Also, Hawk Eye, Mystic Lore, Steel Skin, and Ultimate Strength have leechs effects. How do I fix this? Please help. I don't even know where to start...
